OL,5,G0330 Couples Come Dine with Me
OL,6,     FOn the north Kent coast, the
OL,7,     Fdining contest features an egg
OL,8,     Fphobia, a banter battle, an
OL,9,     Fimpromptu proposal and a haka. And
OL,10,     Fone contestant puts his foot in it
OL,11,     Fwith his own fiancee - twice.
OL,12,G0425 Find It, Fix It, Flog It
OL,13,     FHenry Cole and Simon O'Brien find
OL,14,     Fan old corner cupboard and a pair
OL,15,     Fof outside lanterns to restore in
OL,16,     FSuffolk.
